AttributedTagInterface, ContainedTagInterface, FormElementTagInterface, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, StyledTagInterface, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TryCatchFinally
public class ListFilterButtonHtmlTag
extends FormLinkButtonHtmlTag

Tag that renders the ListWidget's filter form filtering button. Should be used inside list filter form (<ui:listFilter> tag). Button uses label specified by ListWidget—UiLibMessages.LIST_FILTER_BUTTON_LABEL. Also registers enter keyboard handler, so that ENTER key triggers filtering from any filter form field.

Since:
1.0.3
Author:
Oleg MÃ¼rk
Jsp.tag:
name = "listFilterButton" body-content = "JSP" description = "Renders ListWidget's filter form filtering button. Should be used inside <ui:listFilter> tag. Button label identifier is UiLibMessages.LIST_FILTER_BUTTON_LABEL—'uilib.list.filter.button'"
